improved_metadata.title: Bulletproof Thoughts
improved_metadata.description: A lyrical exploration of overcoming challenges with mental fortitude. The song depicts a journey of resilience, facing adversity in an urban landscape, and maintaining focus amidst chaos.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Bulletproof thoughts can't shoot me down
